law.history: Repealed 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 134, sec. 63, effective June 19, 1952. -- Amended 1944 Ky. Acts ch. 88, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1486b-45.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Comparative signature books; comparison of voter's signature with registration record; voting record.
